Skittles has been waiting a whole year for someone to notice how special she is!
Skittles is incredibly sweet and friendly. Despite spending most of her time in a kennel, this beautiful snow white nugget always has a happy grin on her face. She comes to her door to greet anyone who stops by, hoping to go for a walk or just to say hello. Skittles is nervous in the loud shelter though, and we believe this gentle older gal will thrive in a loving home, where she can build her confidence and trust.
Adorable Skittles enjoys going for walks, knows basic commands, and loves treats! She’s 8 years old, a compact 45 lbs, and spayed to go home today! Take Ms. Skittles home, and you’ll have a devoted companion for life!
Life is more colorful with Skittles!
